<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="mathml.xsl"?><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:pref="http://www.w3.org/2002/Math/preference" pref:renderer="mathplayer-dl"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" /><title>glXFreeContextEXT</title><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.69.1" /></head><body><div class="refentry" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="glXFreeContextEXT"></a><div class="titlepage"></div><div class="refnamediv"><h2>Name</h2><p>glXFreeContextEXT — free client-side memory for imported context</p></div><div class="refsynopsisdiv"><h2>C Specification</h2><div class="funcsynopsis"><table border="0" summary="Function synopsis" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="padding-bottom: 1em"><tr><td><code class="funcdef"> void <b class="fsfunc">glXFreeContextEXT</b>(</code></td><td><var class="pdparam">dpy</var>, </td><td> </td></tr><tr><td> </td><td><var class="pdparam">ctx</var><code>)</code>;</td><td> </td></tr></table><table border="0" summary="Function argument synopsis" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td> Display *  </td><td><var class="pdparam">dpy</var>;</td></tr><tr><td> GLXContext  </td><td><var class="pdparam">ctx</var>;</td></tr></table></div></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4781957"></a><h2>PARAMETERS</h2><div class="variablelist"><dl><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>dpy</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specifies the connection to the X server.
                </p></dd><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>ctx</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specifies a GLX rendering context.
                </p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4781866"></a><h2>DESCRIPTION</h2><p>
            <code class="function">glXFreeContextEXT</code> frees the client-side part of a GLXContext that 
            was created with <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glXImportContext</span></span>. <code class="function">glXFreeContextEXT</code> does not 
            free the server-side context information or the XID 
            associated with the server-side context.
        </p><p>
            <code class="function">glXFreeContextEXT</code> is part of the <code class="code">EXT_import_context</code> extension,
            not part of the core GLX command set. If _glxextstring(EXT_import_context)
            is included in the string returned by <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glXQueryExtensionsString</span></span>,
            when called with argument <code class="constant">GLX_EXTENSIONS</code>,
            extension <code class="code">EXT_vertex_array</code> is supported.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4768471"></a><h2>ERRORS</h2><p>
            <code class="constant">GLXBadContext</code> is generated if <em class="parameter"><code>ctx</code></em> does not
            refer to a valid context.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4768490"></a><h2>SEE ALSO</h2><p>
            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glXCreateContext</span></span>,
            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glXQueryVersion</span></span>,
            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glXQueryExtensionsString</span></span>,
            <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glXImportContextEXT</span></span>
        </p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><a id="id4768519"></a><h2>COPYRIGHT</h2><p>
